data.description: SELLER INCENTIVE OFFERED!  Embrace homeownership without the constraints of an HOA in this welcoming 3-bedroom, 2-full bath residence, featuring a fenced-in yard and numerous significant updates. The home, including a new roof and HVAC system installed in December 2022, optimizes its living space with generously sized rooms and ample closets. The spacious eat-in kitchen is highlighted by an abundance of wood cabinets, generous counter space with a peninsula for meal preparation, and seating in the large naturally lit eating area. Additional convenience awaits off the kitchen in the form of a sunlit laundry/mud/storage area, providing access to the two-car garage and a private side-yard exit. Enter the large and inviting living room, showcasing a striking stone wall with an electric fireplace—perfect for relaxing with family and friends. Adjacent to the living room is a versatile space near the main entrance, suitable for dining, office use, a sitting area, or any purpose you desire. Down the hallway, discover the expansive owner's suite with double closets and a well-appointed ensuite featuring double sinks and a walk-in closet. Two additional bedrooms offer ample space and generous-sized closets for family or guests. Enjoy the privacy of the generously sized outdoor patio and the oversized shed located at the rear of the property. This home boasts exceptional curb appeal in the highly sought-after Little River Heights neighborhood of Little River. Revel in the comfort of this residence while benefiting from nearby amenities such as the Intercoastal Waterway, pristine Cherry Grove beach, and excellent dining options. Don't just drive by – call today to schedule your private showing!
